sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant QP as Knative Queue-Proxy<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Caikit as Caikit Runtime<br/>(transformer-container)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>(kserve-container)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(UWM)

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012, mTLS (Istio)
    QP->>Caikit: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>No encryption (same pod)
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
    Caikit-->>QP: HTTP response
    QP-->>IstioGW: Forward response
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>IstioGW: gRPC NlpService call<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward request<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 8012, mTLS
    QP->>Caikit: gRPC(h2c)/8085<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>No encryption (same pod)
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
    Caikit-->>QP: gRPC response
    QP-->>IstioGW: Forward response
    IstioGW-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>HTTPS(h2)/443

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 3: Streaming Text Generation
    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    IstioGW->>QP: Forward (mTLS)
    QP->>Caikit: HTTP/8080 (mTLS)
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC streaming/8033 (localhost)
    loop Token Stream
        TGIS-->>Caikit: Generated token
        Caikit-->>QP: SSE chunk
        QP-->>IstioGW: Forward chunk
        IstioGW-->>Client: SSE event
    end

    Note over Prom,Caikit: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>Plaintext (PERMISSIVE mTLS)
    Caikit-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics

    Note over S3,TGIS: Flow 5: Model Loading (Startup)
    S3-->>TGIS: Model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Secret
    Note right of TGIS: Models loaded to /mnt/models<br/>via KServe storage initializer<br/>or PVC volume mount
